sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3/Minio<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant Pod as Pipeline Step Pod
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over User,API: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission
        User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: OAuth Bearer
        Route->>OAuth: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Service Cert
        OAuth->>API: Forward<br/>HTTP/8888<br/>Bearer Token
        API->>MariaDB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>DB Credentials
        API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Service Account
        API->>MLMD: Log metadata (optional)<br/>gRPC/8080<br/>mTLS if podToPodTLS
        API-->>User: Pipeline created<br/>Response via Route
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over WFC,Pod: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution
        WFC->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Service Account
        K8s-->>WFC: Workflow event
        WFC->>K8s: Create Pipeline Step Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>Service Account
        K8s->>Pod: Start container
        Pod->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTP/9000 or HTTPS/443<br/>S3 Credentials
        S3-->>Pod: Artifacts
        Pod->>Pod: Execute step logic
        Pod->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTP/9000 or HTTPS/443<br/>S3 Credentials
        Pod->>MLMD: Log execution metadata<br/>gRPC/8080<br/>mTLS if podToPodTLS
        Pod->>K8s: Update Workflow status<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>Service Account
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over PA,MariaDB: Flow 3: Status Persistence
        PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Service Account
        K8s-->>PA: Workflow status change
        PA->>MariaDB: Sync execution status<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>DB Credentials
    end

    rect rgb(255, 220, 255)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 4: Artifact Access
        User->>Route: GET /apis/v2beta1/artifacts/{id}<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth Bearer
        Route->>OAuth: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
        OAuth->>API: Forward<br/>HTTP/8888<br/>Bearer Token
        API->>S3: Generate signed URL<br/>HTTP/9000 or HTTPS/443<br/>S3 Credentials
        API-->>User: Signed URL (60s TTL)<br/>Response via Route
        User->>S3: Direct download<br/>HTTP/9000 or HTTPS/443<br/>Signed URL
        S3-->>User: Artifact data
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over User,MariaDB: Flow 5: MLMD Metadata Query
        User->>Route: gRPC call to MLMD Envoy<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth Bearer
        Route->>OAuth: Forward to MLMD Envoy<br/>HTTPS/8443
        OAuth->>MLMD: Forward<br/>gRPC/8080<br/>mTLS if podToPodTLS
        MLMD->>MariaDB: Query metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>DB Credentials
        MariaDB-->>MLMD: Metadata results
        MLMD-->>User: gRPC response<br/>via Route
    end
